# Local development secrets — copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored).
# Public vars (NEXT_PUBLIC_*) live in wrangler.toml [vars] and are committed.
# Server-only secrets go here for local dev, and `wrangler secret put NAME` for production.

# Example secret slots — uncomment when needed:
# REVALIDATE_TOKEN=replace-with-strong-random-string
# INDEXNOW_KEY=replace-with-indexnow-key
